---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import { withBase } from '../utils/paths';
---
<BaseLayout title="Accessibility Statement | Wbbuilt">
  <Hero />

  <section class="section legal" style="padding-top:0">
    <div class="container">
      <p>W B B U I L T is a Melbourne-based construction company specializing in high-end residential, multi-residential, and commercial projects. They focus on delivering complex builds with precision, integrity, and exceptional site management.</p>
      <p>With extensive experience in luxury apartments, bespoke residences, commercial offices, hospitality fit-outs, and education projects, W B B U I L T is trusted to manage technically demanding projects while maintaining high standards of quality, safety, and delivery.</p>
      <p>The company emphasizes storytelling content that reflects their people, processes, craftsmanship, and problem-solving abilities behind the scenes.</p>

      <h2>About WB Built</h2>
      <p>W B B U I L T is committed to creating spaces that inspire. We are dedicated to ensuring that our projects are not only visually stunning but also accessible to people with disabilities, providing equal ease and enjoyment for all visitors.</p>

      <h2>Accessibility</h2>
      <p>At W B B U I L T we believe that web accessibility is fundamental. Our goal is to provide a seamless browsing experience for visitors with disabilities, achieved through adherence to the latest WCAG guidelines and achieving a high level of accessibility. We have implemented various measures to facilitate accessibility, including:</p>

      <h2>Features</h2>
      <p>Our dedication to accessibility is reflected in the following features:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Prioritizing clear and concise content structure</li>
        <li>Providing alternative text for all images</li>
        <li>Ensuring compatibility with assistive technologies such as screen readers and keyboard navigation</li>
        <li>Adhering to optimal color contrast and readability</li>
        <li>Minimizing the use of motion and ensuring all multimedia content is accessible</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Our Physical Accessibility Arrangements</h2>
      <p>WB Built acknowledges that certain pages may have partial compliance due to third-party content, and we are committed to addressing these issues for a fully accessible experience.</p>

      <h2>Physical Accessibility</h2>
      <p>In addition to our digital efforts, WB Built ensures physical accessibility in all our office locations and project sites. Our facilities are equipped with a range of accessibility arrangements, including but not limited to accessible parking, ramps, audio induction loops, and elevators, to ensure a seamless experience for all visitors.</p>

      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you encounter any accessibility issues or have suggestions for improving our website's accessibility, please contact us via the <a href={withBase('/contact')}>contact page</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
